<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.7">
<l>iṟpiṟap paṟiyī rivarava reṉṉī</l>
<l>riṉṉatōrt taṉmaiyeṉ ṟuṇarīr</l>
<l>kaṟpakam pulavar kaḷaikaṇeṉ ṟulakil</l>
<l>kaṇṭavā toṇṭaraip pāṭum</l>
<l>coṟporu ḷāḷīr collukēṉ vammiṉ</l>
<l>cūḻpuṉaṟ kuṭantaiyē toḻumiṉ</l>
<l>naṟporuṭ kāṇmiṉ pāṭinī ruymiṉ</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You do not know [their] place or birth; you cannot say [they are] this one</l>
<l rend="indent">or that one; you do not understand the [true] character of such as these.</l>
<l>You who master words and meaning, who sing of those who serve in the world</l>
<l rend="indent">the way they see [best],</l>
<l>Saying, “Kalpaka [tree]! Sages! Refuge!” come, I will tell you.</l>
<l rend="indent">Worship in water-girded Kuṭantai.</l>
<l>See the true meaning. You save [yourself], singing the name</l>
<l rend="indent">which is pronounced, “Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
